data.description: Welcome to your dream home! Tucked away in this delightful two-story residence, boasting 4 bedrooms and 3 baths, this home spans 2,573 square feet of conditioned space. Including the garage, it totals an impressive 2,684 square feet. Step into the heart of the home and discover a kitchen that's both functional and stunning, featuring under cabinet lighting, quartz countertops, and upgraded matching lighting/chandeliers throughout. Additional amenities include a water softener, under eaves plugs for holiday lighting with a dedicated switch, and USB charging ports in the kitchen and primary bedroom. Experience enhanced comfort and energy efficiency with reflective solar tint on the primary bedroom and 3rd bedroom windows. Notable upgrades continue throughout the home, with a brand-new full metal and noise reduction top-of-the-line modern garage door and opener, complete with two remotes. The garage also includes a pull-up bar and punching bag, ready for your fitness routine. Unwind in the cozy ambiance of the gas community, complemented by an electric warming colorful fireplace with remote control. The loft offers adjustable lighting to set the perfect mood for any occasion. Every detail has been carefully considered, including a bathroom downstairs with a stylish backsplash added on the bottom half of the wall. Nestled on a picturesque cul-de-sac and bordered by a lush green belt, this meticulously maintained residence offers a rare blend of natural beauty and modern comfort. Set on a sprawling lot just under a quarter of an acre, this home is a sanctuary of space and serenity. Plus, enjoy the added convenience of being walking distance to both Sotomayor HS and Scarborough Elementary. You'll love the proximity to grocery stores, shops, hospitals, and restaurants, making everyday errands a breeze. Don't miss the chance to make it yours!
